      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DANCE HER HOME (8) is a super honest type rarely out of the placings, including wins at her last three on end, the latest at this track (22.37). Has an impeccable record here at this journey. Drawn wide but with a clean break will be tough to beat again. ONTARIO (4) has been in super consistent form recently with two minors on end before missing the frame latest finishing fifth (22.56) at this track. Solid record at this trip including seven wins. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and a minor placing from five starts. Can figure in the finish. MERMAID SHIMMER (6) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Grade 4/5/MDN winner (22.38) three back at this track. Can improve sharply here. HERE COMES FOXY (1) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
